This is a gRPC microservice generated by `goboot`.

## Getting Started

### Prerequisites

- Go {{ .GoVersion }}+
- Protocol Buffers compiler (`protoc`)
- Go plugins for `protoc`

### Generating Code

```bash
protoc --go_out=. --go_opt=paths=source_relative \
    --go-grpc_out=. --go-grpc_opt=paths=source_relative \
    api/service.proto
```

### Running the application

```bash
go run cmd/grpc/main.go
```

### API Endpoints

- `Ping`: Simple gRPC ping-pong

## Project Structure

- `api/`: Proto definitions and generated code.
- `cmd/grpc/`: Application entry point.
- `internal/server/`: gRPC server configuration.
- `internal/service/`: Business logic implementation.

